    "description": "<p>Grapes Mental Math inspires future generations with fun and enriching practice-based programmes.</p>\n<p>Besides sharpening your child’s mathematical skills, we also focus on long term brain development and promote higher levels of performance with meaningful and joyous learning experiences.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>WHY US?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>BEST ROUTE TO SUCCESS</p>\n<p>Our Brain Development Program promotes the joy of learning.</p>\n<p>Students are constantly motivated which is the best route to success not only in academics but beyond.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>MAKE LEARNING MATH ENJOYABLE</p>\n<p>Build strong foundational techniques that makes learning math fun and enjoyable.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>DEVELOPMENT OF LEARNING STYLES</p>\n<p>Develop students Kinaesthetic, Auditory and Visual learning styles through our unique multimedia teaching, along with fun and interactive activities.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
